  // Inserting documents into the Employees collection
db.employees.insertMany([
  { "_id": "emp1", "name": "Mr. Patil", "designation": "Software Engineer", "email": "patil@company.com" },
  { "_id": "emp2", "name": "Mr. Sharma", "designation": "Project Manager", "email": "sharma@company.com" },
  { "_id": "emp3", "name": "Ms. Desai", "designation": "Business Analyst", "email": "desai@company.com" },
  { "_id": "emp4", "name": "Mr. Gupta", "designation": "Software Engineer", "email": "gupta@company.com" },
  { "_id": "emp5", "name": "Mr. Reddy", "designation": "QA Engineer", "email": "reddy@company.com" }
]);

// Inserting documents into the Projects collection
db.projects.insertMany([
  { "_id": "proj1", "project_name": "Project A", "project_type": "Development", "start_date": "2024-01-01", "end_date": "2024-06-30", "employee_ids": ["emp1", "emp2", "emp3"] },
  { "_id": "proj2", "project_name": "Project B", "project_type": "Research", "start_date": "2024-03-01", "end_date": "2024-08-31", "employee_ids": ["emp2", "emp4", "emp5"] },
  { "_id": "proj3", "project_name": "Project C", "project_type": "Development", "start_date": "2024-04-01", "end_date": "2024-09-30", "employee_ids": ["emp1", "emp4"] },
  { "_id": "proj4", "project_name": "Project D", "project_type": "Testing", "start_date": "2024-02-15", "end_date": "2024-06-15", "employee_ids": ["emp1", "emp5"] },
  { "_id": "proj5", "project_name": "Project E", "project_type": "Development", "start_date": "2024-05-01", "end_date": "2024-12-01", "employee _ids": ["emp3", "emp4"]})
A.	List all names of projects where Project_type =…..  
  db.projects.find({ "project_type": "Development" }, { "project_name":                 1, "_id": 0 })      

B.	  List all the projects with duration greater than 3 months               
db.projects.find({
  $expr: {
    $gt: [
      { $subtract: [ { $dateFromString: { dateString: "$end_date" } }, { $dateFromString: { dateString: "$start_date" } } ] },
      7884000000  )   ]  }})            
C.	Count no. of employees working on ……..project
db.projects.aggregate([
  { $match: { "project_name": "Project A" } },
  { $project: { _id: 0, project_name: 1, employee_count: { $size: "$employee_ids" } } }])
D.	List the names of projects on which Mr. Patil is working
db.projects.find({ "employee_ids": "emp1" }, { "project_name": 1, "_id": 0 })

      	 
